<article id="post-1284" class="post-1284 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-general category-rants tag-murphys-law">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2009/04/dear-murphy-fuck-off-and-die/" rel="bookmark">Dear Murphy: F*ck off and die!</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Yeah, Murphy, I&#8217;m talking to you.  <br />
You&#8217;ve been dogging me now for 10 months, almost non-stop. You&#8217;ve always been there, hiding in the shadows, popping out every so often to cause a bit of havoc only to vanish again.  <br />
Damned if I know how you did it, but you hid in my luggage or stowed away in the stuff we shipped down from Canada, and moved into my closet. And you&#8217;ve been there ever since. You&#8217;ve come to the office with me every day, haunting my every action, standing over every project. And I&#8217;m sure our hellish daily commute is your doing.<br />
Then then you decided to screw around with my family&#8230;<br />
 <a href="http://geoff.wp/2009/04/dear-murphy-fuck-off-and-die/#more-1284" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> &#8220;Dear Murphy: F*ck off and die!&#8221;</span></a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=49&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r' srcset='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=98&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r 2x' class='avatar avatar-49 photo' height='49' width='49' loading='lazy'/><span class="screen-reader-text">Author </span> <a class="url fn n" href="http://geoff.wp/author/sonworf/">Geoff</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted on </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/2009/04/dear-murphy-fuck-off-and-die/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2009-04-07T21:58:04-06:00">7 April 2009</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Categories </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/category/general/" rel="category tag">General</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/rants/" rel="category tag">Rants</a></span><span class="tags-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Tags </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/murphys-law/" rel="tag">murphy's law</a></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2009/04/dear-murphy-fuck-off-and-die/#comments">2 Comments<span class="screen-reader-text"> on Dear Murphy: F*ck off and die!</span></a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
</article><!-- #post-1284 -->

<article id="post-1212" class="post-1212 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-careers category-children category-costa-rica category-family category-general category-rants category-technology category-travel tag-critical-mass tag-the-hangar tag-year-in-review">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2009/01/2008-a-year-in-review/" rel="bookmark">2008, A Year in Review</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Hasta la vista, 2008! You were a tough year in the life, and while you certainly gave me a good run, I&#8217;m not unhappy to see you go. You&#8217;ve lead me further down the road of fatherhood, brought me back dear old friends, brought me new challenges at work &#8230; and of course moved me to an entirely different country. But with all of this, you&#8217;ve brought a whole mess of turmoil, instability, and grief.  <br />
Now for those of you who&#8217;ve not been following along &#8212; and what the heck, even for those of you have &#8212; here&#8217;s what I&#8217;m talking about: <a href="http://geoff.wp/2009/01/2008-a-year-in-review/#more-1212" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> &#8220;2008, A Year in Review&#8221;</span></a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=49&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r' srcset='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=98&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r 2x' class='avatar avatar-49 photo' height='49' width='49' loading='lazy'/><span class="screen-reader-text">Author </span> <a class="url fn n" href="http://geoff.wp/author/sonworf/">Geoff</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted on </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/2009/01/2008-a-year-in-review/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2009-01-03T12:53:51-07:00">3 January 2009</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Categories </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/category/careers/" rel="category tag">Careers</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/children/" rel="category tag">Children</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/costa-rica/" rel="category tag">Costa Rica</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/family/" rel="category tag">Family</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/general/" rel="category tag">General</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/rants/" rel="category tag">Rants</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/technology/" rel="category tag">Technology</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/travel/" rel="category tag">Travel</a></span><span class="tags-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Tags </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/critical-mass/" rel="tag">critical mass</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/the-hangar/" rel="tag">the hangar</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/year-in-review/" rel="tag">year in review</a></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2009/01/2008-a-year-in-review/#comments">4 Comments<span class="screen-reader-text"> on 2008, A Year in Review</span></a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
