<article id="post-1140" class="post-1140 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-general category-rants tag-calgary tag-canadian tag-copyrights tag-elections tag-law tag-politics">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2008/10/canada-you-can-blame-calgary/" rel="bookmark">Canada, you can blame Calgary</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Sigh.<br />
Well, thanks to the residents of Calgary Centre-North, Canada is now stuck with Jim Prentice <em>again</em>.  And I&#8217;m just too darned tired to rant. Wasted effort at this point.  <br />
But I reserve my right to call &#8220;I told ya so!&#8221; when the lawsuits start.</p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
