		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2007/03/how-not-to-start-a-vacation/" rel="bookmark">How not to start a vacation</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Oy. This vacation is not off to a good start.<br />
One of the conditions of this vacation was that we were to incur no red-eye flights (in other words, no sleeping on the plane). That meant getting there and back was going to cause some difficulty in how we went from Calgary (a second-tier airport) to Kona (a second-to-third tier airport). Direct flight? Hah!<br />
